reviewText: One of the best skateboarding videos
very happy as soon as i got this! every part had and awsome song with it and love the bonus parts.
Good video with some talented skaters. A good skate DVD to add to the collection! Also buy Fully Flared and Yeah Right!
This skate video is an all time classic. Can't go wrong with Toy Machine!!! Thanks Ed Templeton for keeping Toy Machine going for so many years!!!
